David Schwarze			'73 VW Safare Custom Camper (Da Boat)
SAIC Comsystems, San Diego	'73 Capri GT 2800 (Da Beast)
schwarze_at_nosc_dot_mil		'87 Mustang Lx 5.0 (Da Bruiser?  Soon...)
=============================================================================</pre>


